{
  "name": "Sync records between tools with HubSpot and MySQL automatically",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "minutes",
              "minutesInterval": 30
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "8ea75945-70b0-466b-9609-dc660a276832",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        320,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "c0bdb7a7-3c5a-4b10-a4ef-f8c06c7c123b",
              "name": "receivedAt",
              "value": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "1ba16aa6-78cc-4dd1-a248-aba9cbf9f747",
              "name": "isValid",
              "value": "={{ $json ? true : false }}",
              "type": "boolean"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "02fd5ecb-f36c-46db-ae57-356dcf161bc5",
      "name": "Validate Input",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        560,
        300
      ],
      "notes": "Validate & normalize the input before downstream steps (§9.1)."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "contact",
        "operation": "upsert",
        "email": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "additionalFields": {}
      },
      "id": "6df9bf34-5201-4307-957c-38dfbd771e0d",
      "name": "Upsert HubSpot Contact",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.hubspot",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        800,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "8b9c9452-36c3-4c0b-952c-d1334d387fa6",
              "name": "summary",
              "value": "={{ JSON.stringify($json).slice(0, 280) }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "47067d35-5af4-4971-b9be-675b8a58a652",
              "name": "count",
              "value": "={{ $json.items ? $json.items.length : 1 }}",
              "type": "number"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "112c83d1-22b2-4964-b514-2330dea8736a",
      "name": "Edit Fields",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        1040,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Normalize and tag each item\nreturn $input.all().map(i => {\n  i.json.normalized = true;\n  i.json.processedAt = new Date().toISOString();\n  return i;\n});"
      },
      "id": "6eea9ec5-beca-4da4-ab30-75cf7ff67ab1",
      "name": "Transform Items",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1280,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "insert",
        "table": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "records",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "6e8ed877-5c57-4c45-b23e-740674ef341c",
      "name": "Save to MySQL",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.mySql",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [
        1520,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "sms",
        "operation": "send",
        "from": "",
        "to": "={{ $json.phone }}",
        "message": "={{ $json.summary }}"
      },
      "id": "aa09f2c7-1fa9-41cb-916d-07d9937e28c3",
      "name": "Send Twilio Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.twilio",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1760,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Sync records between tools with HubSpot and MySQL automatically\n\n**Pattern:** Two-System Sync\n**Trigger:** Scheduled\n**Integrations:** HubSpot, MySQL, Twilio\n\nImport, add your credentials, then adjust parameters. Original FlowDex template.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 360,
        "color": 4
